attributes.title: Truly Dissatisfied
attributes.review:
I am a huge Trump Supporter and love the idea of making America great again. To become a better American citizen, I decided to get this app to show my support.Most apps take only a few seconds to download, but this app took hours, and took away 70% of my phone charge. I am incredibly and extremely dissatisfied with this app. 
President Donald Trump please do better. I would like to speak with the manager of 
this app. 
🇺🇸📞😤😤😤😤😤😤😤😤😤😤

With anger and disappointment, 
Maryanne Brown
